<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>82</hymn_number>
<title>Kei udi'n Na Thuok</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel gitloh thimah,
 Na hehpihna chanchin;
 Thagau ei panpih in,
 Gen chu ka nuom hi.

[V2]
 Thawkna mak gen sen loh,
 Thing hansedawl chungah;
 Kei dingin na thuok tai,
 Aw.hun chawian zel ka.

[V3]
 2. Zion kulhpi paw-ah,
 Melma'n a hun tuom ui;
 Aw, ka hukdampa chu,
 Na gimthei na e!

[V4]
 3. Isu Na hehpihna,
 Khawvel muntin a hin;
 Gen din ei panpih in,
 Nang dinga vak din.

[V5]
 4. Na hehpihna chanchin,
 Nang nei panpih loh chun;
 Gilote het dingin,
 Ka gen thiem puoh ie.</lyrics>
</song>